title.rendered: Why Can’t I Restore my File?

content.rendered:
If you recently installed an SD card cleaner or storage device cleaner it may be affecting your ability to store files in Dumpster. Any app similar to the following might be affecting Dumpster’s ability to restore:

  • Clean Master
  • DU Battery Saver
  • AVG Cleaner
  • Battery Doctor
  • CCleaner

Add Dumpster to the cleaner’s setting exceptions list.

For additional support, please contact our team by submitting a support ticket in Dumpster. Read here for more information.
